description:

Pageau's youtube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtCTSf3UwRU14nYWr_xm-dQ

Sorting Myself Out youtube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2i_hx_UfauBFh5DA3YWfDg
Follow me on twitter @AndreaLynnLewis
Email me at andreawiththebangs@hotmail.com
